---
title: Spiced Shrimp with Israeli Salad and Lemon-Mint Yogurt Sauce
description: Enjoy a taste of Israel without ever leaving your kitchen thanks to this hearty shrimp salad featuring crisp cucumbers, pearled couscous, and a drizzle of tangy yogurt sauce. Not in the mood to crack open the oven? Make some skewers and toss ‘em on the grill instead!
